a","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9Mp","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":14615,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/06\/dua-tashahhud-allah-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":37597,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Supplication at the end of sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn 'Ubayd reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, heard a man supplicating in his prayer, and he did not send blessing upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cThis man has rushed.\u201d Then, the Prophet called for the man or some others, and he said, \u201cWhen one of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3961,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/oversleeps-misses-forgets-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":37597,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: If someone oversleeps and misses prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: It was mentioned to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, that some of them missed the prayer while they slept and the Prophet said, \u201cIt is not neglectful if missed (unintentionally) because of sleep. Verily, it is only neglectful if missed while awake. If one\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/18\/suicide-funeral-prayer-janazah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37597,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Suicide: Praying over a Muslim who kills himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Samurah reported: A man killed himself and the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, did not pray over him. Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThe people of knowledge disagreed on this issue. Some of them said that the Muslims should perform funeral prayers over every person who prayed towards Mecca,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26737,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/15\/beware-distraction-during-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":37597,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Beware of ruin by distraction in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cO my son, beware of being distracted in prayer, for distraction in prayer is a cause of ruin.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 589 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12945,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/sunan-prayer-before-after-dhuhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":37597,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: The Prophet prays before or after","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: If the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, could not pray four cycles before noon prayer, he would pray them afterwards. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 426 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064f\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0639\u064b\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064f\u0651\u0647\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0647\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37547,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/16\/abandons-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37597,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Whoever abandons the prayer commits unbelief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe covenant between us and them is the prayer, so whoever abandons it has committed unbelief.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 262